messages.message: Hello, I'm working on a derived field that is composed of a custom function. The platform keeps saving the code all the time while I write it. I may be doing something wrong, but this makes it very difficult to advance writing the code, because of the many pauses to save, even if I write a few characters. Is this the expected behavior? Thanks.
what do you mean by “many pauses to save”? are you unable to continue editing the code while the save operation is in progress?
